Package: ggFatFonts
Type: Package
Title: A ggPlot2 plug-in for FatFonts graphics
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Chen Pan, Miguel Nacenta
Maintainer: <Carol.PanChen@outlook.com>
Description: A ggPlot2 plug-in for FatFonts graphics.
    This package helps you build FatFonts graphics on the basis of ggplot2.
    There are currently four quick plot functions provided: ggFFConfMatr, ggFFHeatMap, ggFFCorrMatr and ggFFClusScatPlot.
    Moreover, if you want to build some other plots using FatFonts, you can use addGGFFLayer function.
    There are three FatFonts types available: "Cubica", "Miguta", and "Rotunda".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1)
Imports: ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
